`supabase/` está en `.gitignore`. Contiene Edge Functions (`create-checkout-session`, `create-portal-session`, `stripe-webhook`, `verify-checkout-session`) desplegadas con:

```bash
npm run deploy:checkout
npm run deploy:portal
npm run deploy:webhook
npm run deploy:all
